WEBVTT

00:16:29.971 --> 00:16:34.508
both within our societies
and within ourselves.

00:16:34.532 --> 00:16:38.743
And coming from Turkey,
I do know that the loss of diversity

00:16:38.767 --> 00:16:41.254
is a major, major loss.

00:16:41.278 --> 00:16:44.605
Today, my motherland became
the world's biggest jailer

00:16:44.629 --> 00:16:45.969
for journalists,

00:16:45.993 --> 00:16:49.782
surpassing even China's sad record.

00:16:50.290 --> 00:16:55.684
And I also believe that what happened
over there in Turkey

00:16:55.708 --> 00:16:57.161
can happen anywhere.

00:16:57.185 --> 00:16:59.623
It can even happen here.

00:16:59.647 --> 00:17:03.873
So just like solid countries
was an illusion,